snippet.title: Paper Mario 64K | v3.4.0 Progress Report (Texture Pack - Refolded)
snippet.description:
Note: i recorded the video without the white outline because I haven't added it yet to the texture pack. I'm still working on it.

The texture pack is becoming huge at 4K with each update!
Remember this pack is still in progress so changes might happen.
Thank you for your support!

Release date:
Patrons (4K): Already available (all tiers)
Public (HD): January 10th 2023
